%h2 Typography

-# ========================================
-# Typographic scale

%h4 Scale

%p All font sizes include an extendable class <code>[.]</code>, of which start with <code>h-</code> followed by the font size name. These classes may be used on an element directly or as an extend by way of the <code>@extend</code> rule.

%h6 Hero Scale

%p One off large font sizes to be used for hero, leader, or introduction sections.

%ul.sg-value-list.sg-type-scale
  %li.h-giga
    Giga &ndash; 60px
    %code.sg-value-offset .h-giga
  %li.h-mega
    Mega &ndash; 48px
    %code.sg-value-offset .h-mega

%h6 Default Scale

%p General font sizes used across all headings and default text. The base font size is <code>14</code> pixels.

